    "Here, the authors conclude that the performance of ChatGPT is significantly below that of an average mathematics graduate student.",
    "Similarly, the studies from Huh 29 and Fijačko et al.",
    "30 conclude that ChatGPT could not compete with students in exams on parasitology and life support exams.",
    "However, other studies also show that ChatGPT can pass an English high school exam 31 and a university economics exam 32 with a good grade.",
